56	[Relative cotangent sheaf $\Omega_{X/S}$]
57	  \label{def:relative_kaehler_sheaf}
58	  \lean{AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.relativeDifferentials}
59	  \uses{def:relative_kaehler_presheaf, thm:relative_kaehler_isSheaf}
60	  The sheaf of $\struct{X}$-modules associated with the relative cotangent presheaf is the \emph{sheaf of relative differentials} $\Omega_{X/S}$. It is quasi-coherent.
